headline: Earnings Gains Anticipated In 7 S&P 500 Sectors, Led By Communication Services
summary: Seven of the S&P 500's 11 sectors are expected to achieve cumulative year-over-year growth in normalized earnings per share among their constituent companies in fourth quarter 2024 earnings
